      "name": "技能",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "talent",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">普通攻擊</span></p><p>造成2點<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">物理傷害</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2023/12/21/125391187/ad8a357fa8480f61f3fe665b69d9c263_4950416651509736455.png",
                "id": "talent97789",
                "key": "潛形隱曜弓",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "hydro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "潛形隱曜弓"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素戰技</span></p><p>造成3點<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素傷害</span>，此角色的<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">破局</span>層數+2。</p><p></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2023/12/21/125391187/b0033b9dfbdff746cfb03c7b73792a34_6139512780346834401.png",
                "id": "talent6066",
                "key": "縈絡縱命索",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "hydro"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "縈絡縱命索"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素爆發</span></p><p>造成1點<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素傷害</span>，生成<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">玄擲玲瓏</span>。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">玄擲玲瓏</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">出戰狀態</span></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">我方角色普通攻擊後：</span>造成2點<span style=\"color: #80C0FF\">水元素傷害</span>。</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">持續回合：２</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2023/12/21/125391187/f92e763ec4e356d65ffc75d9443b7d22_7462328210207864506.png",
                "id": "talent93230",
                "key": "淵圖玲瓏骰",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "hydro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "淵圖玲瓏骰"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">破局</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">狀態</span></p><p>此狀態初始具有1層<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">「破局」</span>；重複附屬時，疊加1層<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">「破局」</span>。<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">「破局」</span>最多可以疊加到3層。<br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">結束階段：</span>疊加1層<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">「破局」</span>。</p><p></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">所附屬角色普通攻擊時：</span>如果<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">「破局」</span>已有2層，則消耗2層<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">「破局」</span>，使造成的<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">物理傷害</span>轉換為<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素傷害</span>，並抽1張牌。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2023/12/22/125391187/9c5eb94adf31a35a1dcf456b08342b00_4992509883495896906.png",
                "key": "破局",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "破局"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>附著<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>，可發生元素反應：</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">蒸發</span>：本傷害+2</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">感電</span>：本傷害+1，對目標以外的所有敵方角色造成1點<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">穿透傷害</span></p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">冰元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">凍結</span>：本傷害+1，使目標本回合無法行動（受到<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">物理</span>或<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>傷害后提前解除，但是傷害+2）</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">草元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">綻放</span>：本傷害+1，生成使下次<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>或<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>傷害+2的<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">「草原核」</span></p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">草原核</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">出戰狀態</span></p><p>我方對敵方出戰角色造成<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素傷害</span>或<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素傷害</span>時，傷害值+2。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次數：1</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2023/12/22/125391187/a126c6a302d81c07e19cf9a9f1260f90_1716044878123158361.png",
                "key": "水元素傷害",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "水元素傷害"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">物理傷害</span></strong></p><p>物理傷害不會附著元素，也不會發生元素反應。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次數</span></strong></p><p>此牌效果觸發後，會消耗一層<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次數</span>；</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次數</span>耗盡後，立刻棄置此牌。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2023/12/22/125391187/07bae546ac7c69ef6402170b283840c5_8845976403391021019.png",
